Name: path and name of the source file
Description:
.stabs "path_name", N_SO, NIL, NIL, Code_address_of_program_start
.stabs "file_name:", N_SO, NIL, NIL, Code_address_of_program_start

Name: Line Numbers
Description:
symbol: 
.stabn N_SLINE, NIL, source line, address(label for the start of source line)

Name:
Procedures
(f: local/F: global)
Description:
.stabs "name: desc (global proc `F') return_type_ref (int)",
N_FUN, NIL, NIL, address
exp:  .stabs "main:F1",36,0,0,_main

Name:
block structure
(left/right brace大括号)
Description:
(The label that describe the start/end block  just follows the N_FUNC stab describing the procedure ifself)
.stabn N_LBRAC, NIL, NIL, left-brace-address(label)
.stabn N_RBRAC, NIL, NIL, right-brace-address(label)
